* ATMOD = 10 allows to change all atmosphere
* User exponetial function as linear
ATMOD 10
ATMLAY 4e+05  10e+05  40e+05  1.12e+07
ATMA   -1.02348092e+05 -1.02348092e+05  -1.02348092e+05  -1.02348092e+05 1.03086513e+03
